 Eve and are now ready to take on 2013. I know I am. I follow various life-hacking or so called &#8220;self improvement&#8221; blogs and read on a few of them about the importance of writing down your [...]</p><p><a href=\"http://dannyvankooten.com/802/goals-for-2013/\">Goals for 2013</a></p>\";s:7:\"content\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";s:2431:\"<p>Boy, does time fly. Anyway, happy new year for all of you! Hope you had a blast during New Year&#8217;s Eve and are now ready to take on 2013. I know I am.</p>\n<p>I follow various life-hacking or so called &#8220;self improvement&#8221; blogs and read on a few of them about the importance of <a href=\"http://fitzvillafuerte.com/the-importance-of-writing-down-your-goals-on-paper.html\">writing down your goals</a> and sharing them with others. That&#8217;s why I will use this post to list my goals for 2013. I will come back throughout 2013 and update it when I made any goal related progress.</p>\n<h3>Work related goals</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Release and offer support for a total of 5 WordPress plugins with each of them having over 10k downloads by the end of this year (3/5)</li>\n<li>Create a Dutch portfolio website with all my client work</li>\n<li>Create a new WordPress theme for this website</li>\n<li>Release either a premium WordPress plugin OR a premium WordPress theme</li>\n<li>Stick to / focus on creating (responsive) WordPress themes when it comes to client work</li>\n<li>Take on more (of the above) client work</li>\n<li>Become a JavaScript expert (too broad or vague, I know)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Study goals</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Finish an internship assignment for a movie production company based in Bangkok</li>\n<li>Follow a minor in entrepeneurship</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Travel goals</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Travel, work, orientate and enjoy life in Asia for at least a few months. (planned)</li>\n<li>Visit at least 1 more country in the second part of 2013</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Fitness goals</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Deadlift 2.5x BW. (2.1/2.5)</li>\n<li>Squat 2x BW (1.61 / 2)</li>\n<li>Overhead Press 1x BW (0.67 / 1)</li>\n<li><del>Bench Press 1x BW (1 / 1)</del></li>\n<li>12 consecutive body weight pull-ups</li>\n<li>20 consecutive body weight dips</li>\n<li>Drink less beer (have less hangovers)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>That is all I can come up with at the moment. All of these goals seem pretty clear to me, are definitely attainable, inspire me and have a deadline. These are not new year resolutions, these are mere items on a to do list.</p>\n<p>Did you set your goals for 2013 already? Tell me about them in the comments cause sharing goals is important, remember?!</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://dannyvankooten.com/802/goals-for-2013/\">Goals for 2013</a></p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/dannyvankooten/~4/0ctlQGGXKSA\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>\";}s:3:\"wfw\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentrss\";s:50:\"http://dannyvankooten.com/802/goals-for-2013/feed/\";}s:5:\"slash\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";s:1:\"2\";}s:10:\"feedburner\";a:1:{s:8:\"origlink\";s:45:\"http://dannyvankooten.com/802/goals-for-2013/\";}s:7:\"summary\";s:399:\"<p>Boy, does time fly. Anyway, happy new year for all of you! Hope you had a blast during New Year&#8217;s Eve and are now ready to take on 2013. I know I am. I follow various life-hacking or so called &#8220;self improvement&#8221; blogs and read on a few of them about the importance of writing down your [...]</p><p><a href=\"http://dannyvankooten.com/802/goals-for-2013/\">Goals for 2013</a></p>\";s:12:\"atom_content\";s:2431:\"<p>Boy, does time fly. Anyway, happy new year for all of you! Hope you had a blast during New Year&#8217;s Eve and are now ready to take on 2013. I know I am.</p>\n<p>I follow various life-hacking or so called &#8220;self improvement&#8221; blogs and read on a few of them about the importance of <a href=\"http://fitzvillafuerte.com/the-importance-of-writing-down-your-goals-on-paper.html\">writing down your goals</a> and sharing them with others. That&#8217;s why I will use this pos